{"tid":1939782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】不滿中国隱瞞疫情 土耳其大學生醞釀集體索償","createTime":"2020-03-23T10:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T10:17:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"48c453f0a14aeb834b60a68087ff41823fc3f8db","tid":1939782,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎全球大爆發，繼早前美國佛羅里達州4名民眾集體入稟控告包括中國政府、國家衞健委、國家緊急管理部、民政部、湖北省政府，以及武漢市政府未能及時控制疫情，要求索償後，中央社也訪問到一名土耳其大學生，他上周已致函中國駐土耳其大使館，要求中國政府承擔隱瞞疫情的責任並「賠償」。媒體披露後，許多本地學生也打算集體要求中國賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200323/XYLR3QNJPGZANEHZFGV6MU2N2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200323%2FXYLR3QNJPGZANEHZFGV6MU2N2Y%2F&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfrw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=58deb2b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200323%2FXYLR3QNJPGZANEHZFGV6MU2N2Y%2F&h=2d3dc4bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200323/XYLR3QNJPGZANEHZFGV6MU2N2Y/</a>"},{"pid":"3dd19ed50cd632ef15282adb28cd54df218fd8ac","tid":1939782,"uid":274723,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:38:07.000Z","msg":"土耳其咁心水清架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好戲在後頭"},{"pid":"066fa5723cab9ac5c32b92cb6c11d2ddc872156c","tid":1939782,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"89a8730fb3babc3fda18dbf269a4b75f60eccc9e","tid":1939782,"uid":347723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:43:36.000Z","msg":"【網絡安全】點解手足仲用緊Whatsapp同Telegram?! 用吓呢啲App好無?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1927662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1927662</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"930aa06861a9dfe9035c1750bdd3e8afae4a8532","tid":1939782,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:43:53.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/asse